    python-support (>= 0.90)
Standards-Version: 3.9.1

Package: python-multitail2
Architecture: all
Depends:
    ${python:Depends},
    ${misc:Depends},
    python-six
Description: Python module for following multiple files at once
 Like `tail -f` for python, but it supports accepting a glob spec like
 '/var/log/*.log' and it adds, removes and reopens files as they are
 created, deleted, and rotated.
